Package: wx_archive
Title: Create and Maintain an Archive of 2-hourly Data from Three NOAA Forecast Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Dean", "Koch", , "koch@yellowstoneresearch.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8849-859X"))
Description: This collects 2-hourly data from the following (NOAA) forecast models:  Rapid Update Cycle (RUC) from 2005 to 2007 (26km resolution); Rapid Refresh (RAP) from 2007 to present less 2 days (13km resolution); and Global Forecast System (GFS) from 10 days before present to 5 days ahead (28km resolution). It builds a completed archive (extending 5 days into the future) with all missing times imputed.
